# VR Info

Tags: [[Virtual Reality]]

# Before Setup

1. Charge controllers.
1. Set up equipment used to ground out of reality, such as a fan or a mat.

# Warnings

1. Do NOT expose lenses to sunlight.
1. If feeling ill, stop playing and take the headset off.
1. Ensure that all reflective surfaces (mirrors, blank screens, glossy posters) are removed from play space or covered.

